title: Money Movers (New Episode)
overview: Money Movers provides investors with real-time analysis of the stories and the people attracting the attention of the markets each day. Capturing the energy of day's early trading, the program includes the breaking news and numbers driving stocks and sectors, helping investors make critical decisions. "Money Movers" anchors Carl Quintanilla and Sara Eisen speak with the CEOs, government decision-makers and newsmakers who play a relevant role in how money is moving.
